`‚òÖ Insight ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ`
- **Nested `<Modal>` in React Native** works reliably ‚Äî SettingsScreen's own `Modal` sits on top of PauseMenu's `Modal` without any portal/navigation setup needed. React Native renders modals in a separate top-level view layer.
- **Bottom-sheet pattern without libraries**: `animationType="slide"` + `justifyContent: "flex-end"` + `maxHeight: "90%"` on the content + a handle-bar indicator gives a native-feeling bottom sheet with zero extra dependencies.
- **Step-based controls vs sliders**: With no `@react-native-community/slider` installed, +/‚àí Pressable buttons give guaranteed 44px touch targets and are fully accessible via `accessibilityRole="button"`. The progress track is a pure View, not a draggable ‚Äî simpler and just as readable for this settings UI.
`‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ`

